---
import Bi from '../shared/Bi.astro';
import Callout from '../shared/Callout.astro';
import Section from '../mechanics/Section.astro';
---
<Section id="settling" titleZh="第 1 階段：盡快開到第 2 村" titleEn="Phase 1: Settle the 2nd village ASAP" eyebrow="Lumi §1">
  <p>
    <Bi
      zh="開局唯一目標：第 2 村。為什麼急著開？因為糧食是 Travian 中 ROI 最高的資源，而首都（Lv11–20 解鎖）才是真正的產糧引擎。從定居村轉到「真正的首都」越早越好。"
      en="The only opening goal: get village #2. Why the rush? Crop is the highest-ROI resource in Travian, and the capital (with Lv11–20 fields unlocked) is the real crop engine. The sooner you settle off the spawn village, the sooner the snowball begins."
    />
  </p>

  <h3><Bi zh="拿一份開村指南" en="Use a settling guide" /></h3>
  <p>
    <Bi
      zh="不要自己摸索。每個族都有最佳化過的時間表（依 1x 速度寫的）。羅馬可以雙隊伍佔便宜；高盧開拓者最便宜；條頓可以靠掠奪補資源。每一族的最佳順序略有差異，但骨幹相同：田地 → 主府 → 居所 → 慶典 → 開拓者。"
      en="Don't wing it. Every tribe has a battle-tested timeline (calibrated for 1x speed). Romans abuse the dual queue, Gauls have the cheapest settlers, Teutons fund settlement via raiding. Each tribe's exact sequence differs slightly, but the spine is identical: fields → Main Building → Residence → celebrations → settlers."
    />
  </p>

  <h3><Bi zh="第 2 村目標時間" en="Target settlement time" /></h3>
  <ul>
    <li><Bi zh="羅馬 / 高盧：Day 5–6 開到第 2 村" en="Romans / Gauls: village #2 by Day 5–6" /></li>
    <li><Bi zh="條頓：Day 6–7（兵養家難度高一點）" en="Teutons: Day 6–7 (slightly harder due to troop investment)" /></li>
    <li><Bi zh="埃及 / 匈人：Day 6–8（兵 / 建築週期較重）" en="Egyptians / Huns: Day 6–8 (heavier troop / building cycles)" /></li>
  </ul>

  <Callout kind="tip" titleZh="慢開可能反而更好" titleEn="Sometimes slower start = better start">
    <p>
      <Bi
        zh="Lumi 提到：刻意晚 1–8 小時開帳號，會被 spawn 在地圖外圍，比較少人跟你搶綠洲。前期靠英雄打綠洲動物的收入巨大，少一個競爭者差很多。"
        en="Per Lumi: deliberately starting 1–8 hours after server launch puts you closer to the map edge, with fewer competitors for early oases. Hero oasis-clearing income is enormous early on; one fewer rival per oasis matters."
      />
    </p>
  </Callout>
</Section>
